      },
      "date": "2015-11-25 01:05:25.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(4 comments)\n\nPlease do not submit all of these unrelated patches as a single series. Each one should be on a separate branch when it is pushed, unless it has a dependency on the previous patch.\n\nOtherwise, it is difficult to land the patches independently if one of them has a testing problem or needs to be refreshed for some reason. That would force all of the patches after it to be refreshed also, which is cumbersome.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
